This is the Show view for a particular user. Their name is 
<%= @user.name %>
When fleshed out this will also show their profile, but make sure only that user can EDIT the profile!

<turbo-frame id="edit_account">
  <%= link_to "Edit My Account", edit_user_registration_path %>
</turbo-frame>

<turbo-frame id="edit_profile">
  <%= link_to "Edit Profile Info.", edit_profile_path(id: @profile.id) %>
  HERE THE PROFILE INFO IS DISPLAYED AND CAN BE EDITED USING THE TURBO FRAME
  <%= image_tag(@profile.picture, width: 200) if @profile.picture.attached? %>
</turbo-frame>
